Module kivakit.core.kernel

Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.language.values.mutable

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MutableIndex
    A mutable index value for use in lambdas and anonymous inner classes.
    MutableInteger
    An integer value that can be changed.
    MutableLong
    A long value that can be changed.
    MutableValue<T>
    A value that can be retrived with MutableValue.get() and mutated with MutableValue.set(Object) or MutableValue.update(Function).
